said.
   The two men were not identified.
   TV Globo, the nation's largest private network, said the
building's porter surprised the two men during an apparent burglary
of the apartment, and the two then grabbed the hostages and made
their demands.
   The two surrendered after authorities promised them they could
meet with a lawyer, the network said.
   Torres was in New York at the time.
