<DATELINE>MUENSTER, West Germany (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A district official in North
Rhine-Westphalia has been accused of embezzling $4.7 million to buy
antique cars, toy soldiers and teddy bears, authorities said.
   They said an investigation showed the 37-year-old man, who was
